QUOTABLE

"If we put a roadblock in front of exporting to countries like
Canada, it's going to have to come to places like Alabama. We
have enough waste in Alabama. We don't want anymore. We want it
to go somewhere else."

--Rep. Sonny Callahan (R-Ala.) speaking at the first hearing this
year before the House Energy and Commerce subcommittee on
transportation and hazardous materials regarding reauthorization
of the Resource Conservation and Recovery Act (RCRA).




