     Michael Grubb's paper "The Greenhouse Effect: Negotiating
Targets" (see this issue's Focus Report) is available for 10 pounds
(including postage) from The Royal Institute of International
Affairs.  Call TEL: +44-1-930-2233 to order a copy... An
